John Lewis UK store sales up 11 . 3 % y / y latest week . The John Lewis Partnership JLP . CN said its UK weekly department store sales rose 11 . 3 percent in the week to July 5 from the same week a year earlier . In the 23 weeks to July 5 , sales were up 10 . 1 percent . Total sales , including the Waitrose supermarket group , rose 7 . 5 percent in the latest week and 7 . 0 percent in the 23 week period . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 7708 
